00:21:00,667 --> 00:21:09,453
I mean, I know what I would like to see is I'd love to see just a timeline of events, literally from when this whole issue came about.

233
00:21:10,370 --> 00:21:14,754
when the list got messed up and people were deleted, people added back on.

234
00:21:14,814 --> 00:21:17,557
I mean, who gave that person the authority to do that?

