244
00:21:38,531 --> 00:21:42,752
Because I know I have a ton of questions, as I'm sure my colleagues do as well.

245
00:21:42,832 --> 00:21:46,353
But there are a lot of things, I think, that need to be looked at.

246
00:21:47,633 --> 00:21:49,093
It's very frustrating.

247
00:21:49,133 --> 00:21:52,374
Here we are a month later, and we're doing this.

