00:21:54,774 --> 00:21:56,655
It'll be next Wednesday.

250
00:21:56,775 --> 00:21:57,455
Thank you very much.

251
00:21:57,475 --> 00:21:57,995
I appreciate it.

252
00:21:58,255 --> 00:21:58,495
Thank you.

